snippet.title: Celestial Heights - Game Made in 48 Hours!
snippet.description:
I made a game about using a grappling hook to reach the top of a building for the Ludum Dare 49 compo.
Play it here (HTML5 / Windows / Linux): https://shp.itch.io/celestial-heights
